name: Johnson's Baby Cooling Powder (200g)
description:
DESCRIPTION



With natural honeysuckle extract. Clinically proven mild. Dermatologist-tested. We love babies. And we understand how important it is for you to keep your baby cool and comfortable. That’s why JOHNSON’S® Baby Cooling Powder is enriched with natural honeysuckle and a delicate fragrance, to help your baby’s skin stay cool and fresh. It instantly cools the skin and lower skin temperature in less than 1 minute.



Best for Baby. Best for you.



HOW TO USE



Shake powder onto your hand before applying to baby’s skin. Close tightly after use.



Keep powder away from children’s nose and mouth to avoid inhalation, which can cause breathing problems. Avoid contact with eyes.



For external use only. Do not use on broken skin.



INGREDIENTS



Talc, fragrance, Isopulegol, Lonicera Japonica (Honeysuckle) Flower Extract
